<L>__{interior alex's house night}
<A>__{alex releases his barking german shepherd and it immediately attacks david, biting his leg. david screams in agony.}
<C>__{john}
<P>__{(to alex)}
<D>__{back up! get back!}
<A>__{suddenly a thug comes barreling in from the kitchen and aims a sawed off shotgun at john, who keeps himself right behind david's head. the dialogue is almost drowned out completely by the sound of pounding in john's ears and david's screaming.}
<C>__{alex}
<D>__{ shoot them both!}
<C>__{john}
<D>__{ i will shoot the dog!}
<C>__{alex}
<D>__{ shoot the dog!}
<C>__{thug}
<D>__{ you shoot the dog, i will kill you!}
<A>__{john fires into the floor beside the dog.}
<C>__{alex}
<D>__{ you want the police here, asshole?!}
<C>__{john}
<D>__{ good idea!}
<A>__{john fires two more shots into the floor.}
<C>__{alex}
<P>__{(to thug)}
<D>__{ put the gun down!}
<A>__{the thug obeys, rests it against the wall.}
<C>__{john}
<D>__{ call the dog off!! put it away!}
<C>__{alex}
<D>__{ release!}
<A>__{the dog stops its attack but goes back to barking.}
<C>__{john}
<D>__{ put it away!!}
<P>__{(aims gun at it)}
<D>__{put it away!!}
<A>__{alex reluctantly opens a closet door.}
<C>__{alex}
<D>__{in! get in!}
<A>__{he has to shove the barking dog into the closet.}
<C>__{john}
<P>__{(to thug)}
<D>__{you, too!}
<C>__{thug}
<D>__{i'm not getting in there!}
<A>__{john fires into the wall!}
<C>__{alex}
<D>__{get in!}
<A>__{and the thug goes in the closet after the barking dog. john sees the bolt and drives it home, locking the door.}
<C>__{john}
<D>__{ give me that chair!}
<A>__{alex doesn't obey, so david grabs it and hands it to him. john props it under the handle of the closet door.}
<C>__{john }
<D>__{move!}
<A>__{he shoves david forward, closer to alex.}
<C>__{alex}
<D>__{you're dead.}
<C>__{david}
<D>__{i didn't do anything!!}
<C>__{alex}
<D>__{you brought him!}
<C>__{david}
<D>__{i didn't bring him!}
<C>__{john}
<D>__{shut up!}
<A>__{he pushes them both back into the next room; the dog in the closet never stops barking.}
